    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the 'Polestar' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, and the completion of a long cruise aboard a capital ship.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "装备上这枚专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">个人天赋</span>，纪念你完成“极星”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>并完成了主力飞船上的漫长航行。<br><br>在外观修改器<span class=\"name name-technology\">中将这面旗帜应用至你的个人档案</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "裝備這款特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">個人造型</span>紀念「北極星」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>的完成，以及在主力太空船上進行長途巡航的榮耀。<br><br>在外觀改造器<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>將此旗幟套用至你的檔案。"
  },
